title: 2014 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 56)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
2014 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

We have now finally accounted for music uploaded, and/or downloaded from Christian Tunes during the month of September.  This torrent contains the last of that music, along with a few additional titles (to round out the two gig bundle limit) that may be new to some of you.

Thank you to everyone who has been able to help me seed these past few days.  Every little bit helped.  And thank you to all of you who stick around and continue to share this music with others, after I've moved onto the next bundle.

I'm looking forward to the 57th bundle for a couple of reasons.  It will represent equaling the number of bundles we shared amongst ourselves back in 2013.  It will contain more music that may be new to many of you.  It will mean I am finally caught up, and so too will you be.

CHRISTMAS: Guy Penrod, Michael W Smith, Various Christmas.  PRAISE & WORSHIP: Shane And Shane, Various Revelation, Victory World Church Worship.  SINGER-SONGWRITER: Various Body, Various Song.  ROCK: Various Nashville.  INSTRUMENTAL Various Reflections.  CONTEMPORARY: Various Sing, Various Urban.  BLUES: Various Blues.  CHILDREN: Vineyard.

We have 14 titles to choose from today, including...

 * Guy Penrod - 2014 - Christmas
 * Michael W Smith - 2014 - The Spirit Of Christmas
 * Shane And Shane - 2014 - The Worship Initiative, Vol 8
 * Various - 2014 - Body Weather
 * Various - 2014 - Christmas Elegance - Instrumentals For Peaceful Holiday Season
 * Various - 2014 - Nashville Publicity Group Presents Ten
 * Various - 2014 - Reflections Dramatic
 * Various - 2014 - Revelation Song - 11 Essential Worship Songs
 * Various - 2014 - Sing Over Me - The Songs Of Dennis Jernigan
 * Various - 2014 - The Blues And Salvation
 * Various - 2014 - The Song Album - Music From The Motion Picture
 * Various - 2014 - Urban Legends, Vol 1
 * Victory World Church Worship - 2014 - Covered
 * Vineyard - 2014 - Great Big God 5 - Ready To Go

God Bless,
TorrentTracts, October 2014
